{"tid":1040002,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"數碼鋼琴多選一困難症","createTime":"2019-02-27T20:45:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T02:29:07.000Z","uid":166618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"895d993933e42b1d47572b512cf925e0c100a157","tid":1040002,"uid":166618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T20:45:59.000Z","msg":"本身筆直就$10000 但愈睇愈多發現揀上去好似多幾千差好大分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n學左一年，中意夜晚彈，之前有部二手鋼琴但真係好多時都唔方便彈<br />\n<br />\n想買YAMAHA CLP-635/645/545，因為比起625成個外觀似鋼琴D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  牌子純粹係品牌信心<br />\n<br />\n上reddit d人講木鍵差別好大，但645真係太over筆直，想問545會唔會差好多？<br />\n<br />\n如果唔會，會嘗試搵下有冇其他鋪頭有，又擔心鋼琴買水貨會唔會比起其他電子野冇咁安全？<br />\n<br />\n另外網上有部二手545 筆直內，但係唔知點check，我應該可以叫到鋼琴老師幫手上門睇<br />\n<br />\n怕佢只彈開真鋼琴都未必容易check到二手數碼鋼琴有冇問題<br />\n<br />\n定係數碼鋼琴一壞就會成個鍵或者音壞到好誇張無聲／走晒音好明顯，肯定要維修咁？<br />\n<br />\n求巴絲打們指點迷津呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf06148c8dff55fe0e9f424d027b4299953f7fb5","tid":1040002,"uid":166618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇巴打熟數碼鋼琴？"},{"pid":"246e15f676fa0b5cdef25e66320f409f2cd5698c","tid":1040002,"uid":14715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T20:36:12.000Z","msg":"Yamaha P515 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n性價比算係中高階琴最高"},{"pid":"c01756b89a569565ce3beb983d4a4709db2ad382","tid":1040002,"uid":170160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T02:29:07.000Z","msg":"點解唔考慮 ROLAND ? 個人覺得琴鍵手感比 YAMAHA 好 !"}]}